I still do.

1092
01:17:27,844 --> 01:17:30,844
2人でデビュー直後、不安なことを語り
Do you remember walking together at night

1093
01:17:30,844 --> 01:17:33,344
夜道を歩いたの覚えてますか？
after debut, talking about our anxieties?

1094
01:17:33,544 --> 01:17:36,844
歩いた。歩いたね。
We did. We walked, didn't we?

1095
01:17:37,544 --> 01:17:41,844
その時の相談事とかあったと思うんですけど...
I think we had a lot to talk about back then...

1096
